## Constraints

### Use

- Zod schemas from `@leanmgmt/shared-schemas` (define here if not yet)
- JWT HS256 + config.jwtAccessSecretCurrent (env)
- Refresh rotation + family tracking (`docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION` Bölüm 3.3)
- bcrypt cost 12 + dummy hash timing protection
- Error codes per taxonomy (`AUTH_INVALID_CREDENTIALS`, etc.)
- Rate limits:
  - Login: 10/min IP + 5/15min email
  - Password reset: 3/hour email
  - Refresh: 30/min user
- PII middleware for email (det) + phone (probab)

### Avoid

- MFA (scope out of MVP)
- SSO / federated auth (post-MVP)
- Password policy configurability (hardcode per spec)
- Client-side JWT parsing (server /auth/me kullan)
- localStorage for tokens (memory Zustand)
- Session cookie (only refresh token cookie)

