## Explicit Don'ts

- MFA implementation — roadmap Wave 1
- Password policy configurable — hardcode 12+ char rules
- JWT secret in code — env only
- Logging tokens/passwords (Pino redaction)
- Skip timing-attack protection "test için"
- `/auth/me` caching frontend'te (always fresh)
- Alternative session mechanism (cookie-only, stateful session)

## Related ADRs

- ADR-0008: JWT HS256 over RS256
- ADR-0009: Refresh token family tracking (theft detection)
- ADR-0010: bcrypt cost 12 + timing-attack protection
- ADR-0011: Deterministic email encryption (lookup + KVKK)
- ADR-0012: Access token memory-only, refresh httpOnly cookie

